data.description:
Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath home that is only 1 year old and 
conveniently located near downtown and the University of Tennessee.  As you walk inside, the open floor plan allows for plenty of natural light to flow throughout the home, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere.  Also you'll be delighted by a spacious kitchen area with beautiful wood slab countertops...perfect for entertaining or enjoying family meals. With its inviting design and convenient  location, this house is sure to impress! Plenty of storage and workshop possibilities in the soaring  basement area. See it today!!
